name: Unidentified_Aqualish_(Abafar)
content:
This Aqualish lived on the remote planet of Abafar around 20 BBY, in the city of Pons Ora. As the D-Squad was strolling around in the city, this Aqualish was seen spitting into a bucket.
According to StarWars.com "Missing in Action" Trivia Gallery, this Aqualish was designed to resemble the Kenner action figure of Ponda Baba, nicknamed "Walrus Man", first introduced in Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope.
